value.name: What exactly happened to Louise's first husband in Arrival?
value.snippet: Louise only had one husband - Ian Donnelly - the scientist she worked with in communicating with the aliens. What happens is that Louise ends up realizing that the visions she has of her daughter are in the future, not the past. After the incident with the aliens, she marries Ian, has a daughter, and then watches her daughter die from cancer.
